    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for someone looking for a functional driver at a reasonable price point. The exterior has several visible scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension check-up in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that isn't perfect but still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
